        public void setTypes(MgIntCollection types)
        Sets the geometry type value list. Elements must be integers as defined by MgGeometryType.
        Parameters:
        types - (MgIntCollection*) The collection of types. There must be no more than MG_MAX_GEOMETRY_TYPE_SIZE elements.
